16
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:39,000
If you think it's so easy, then get online and try to beat me.

17
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:39,000
Fine.

18
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:53,000
Damn it!

19
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:56,000
