20
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:56,000
It's not fair!

21
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:58,000
I don't want to play anymore.

22
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:00,000
Let's go get something to eat.

23
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,000
Can you bring me something?

24
